\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

's expected profit if he accepts a buyer with signal 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

, and let 
\begin_inset Formula $V(y)$
\end_inset

 be the average profit flow when a seller of type 
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

 acts optimally (the value function)
